<h2 id="ID-8abb8916-289a-44a1-9a4d-1ec3ebe0d8ab">How to do multiple choice in yasnippet</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org47ae941">
<p>
Example from the blog
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-yasnippet"># -*- mode: snippet -*-
# name: test
# key: test
# --
Importance: ${1:$$(yas-choose-value '("high" "average" "below average"))}
Difficulty: ${2:$$(yas-choose-value '("easy" "hard"))}
$0
</pre>
</div>
